1
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:28,200
♪Confessing to the moon
in the rustling wind back then♪

2
00:00:28,200 --> 00:00:34,440
♪Like a boat being swallowed up
among the cities♪

3
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:41,440
♪Watching the flowers fall in unease,
worries and troubles fill my mind♪

4
00:00:42,080 --> 00:00:48,240
♪Am I going to where I want♪

5
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:50,960
♪To stay or to leave, you decide♪

6
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:54,960
♪Nations are different♪

7
00:00:55,280 --> 00:01:01,520
♪One without desire
is one that is not alive♪

8
00:01:02,120 --> 00:01:04,560
♪Looking at the sky side by side♪

9
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:08,320
♪We've gotten closer with time♪

10
00:01:08,320 --> 00:01:15,120
♪One glance,
the city of Chang'an is bare♪

11
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:22,360
♪Among the ridiculous people
and things is me♪

12
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:30,360
=Dream of Chang'An=

13
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:33,080
=Episode 39=

14
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:36,880
Madam Li!

15
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:39,840
Madam Li! What's wrong?

16
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:40,680
Madam Li!

17
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:55,680
I'll avenge Madam Li!

18
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:56,520
Stop!

19
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,520
Qiu Yanzhi...

20
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:07,640
Why did you do it?

21
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,240
Qiu Yanzhi...

22
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:12,400
Xiu.

23
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,160
Why must you kill Madam Li?

24
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,320
She only wanted

25
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,160
to tell me who I really am!

26
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,320
Ling Ling.

27
00:02:23,160 --> 00:02:23,840
I know

28
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,520
you want your doubt answered.

29
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,960
But if you kill me now,

30
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:28,080
you will never leave

31
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,120
with your life.

32
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:32,880
Think about His Majesty.

33
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:35,240
Think about the Xing empire
he wants to rebuild.

34
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,160
For the sake of this nation,

35
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:40,280
we must stay alive.

36
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,880
I got reckless

37
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,040
and killed Li Rong.

38
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:41,000
Is there a way to remedy this?

39
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,360
Li Rong may be gone,

40
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,560
but Cheng Xi will come after us.

41
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:48,680
We should figure out a way

42
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,000
to stop her

43
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,560
from seeing Ruoling again

44
00:03:51,760 --> 00:03:53,720
rather than remedy this.

45
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,720
Handle it with care.

46
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:34,640
Your Majesty.

47
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:36,720
Ling Ling has invited you

48
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:38,960
to meet at Ziyu Pavilion tomorrow night.

49
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:47,680
What was that?

50
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:49,520
Ling Ling has invited you

51
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:52,600
to meet at Ziyu Pavilion tomorrow night.

52
00:05:06,980 --> 00:05:09,780
(For His Majesty's Inspection Only)

53
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:11,960
I knew it.

54
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:15,880
I chased you away time and time again,

55
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,720
but you always come back.

56
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:15,500
(For His Majesty's Inspection Only)

57
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:18,700
(Chess of Generals Camp)

58
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:20,880
Madam Li.

59
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:25,160
You were killed because of me.

60
00:06:44,140 --> 00:06:49,754
♪When a fish swims to the surface♪

61
00:06:49,755 --> 00:06:54,780
♪Who else will swim in the deep end♪

62
00:06:56,340 --> 00:07:01,958
♪When the wind and rain
empty the long scale♪

63
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:07,700
♪Who will still go to work early
and return late after being drenched♪

64
00:07:08,020 --> 00:07:13,140
♪Some have longings♪

65
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:13,840
Care for a drink?

66
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:17,600
I don't want to see your face right now.

67
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,440
Leave.

68
00:07:20,499 --> 00:07:26,185
♪With no arguments, there are no lies♪

69
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:31,578
♪But the battlefield didn't teach me
to distinguish between them yet♪

70
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:37,880
♪Who says I never made a wish♪

71
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,120
I know that

72
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:42,040
Li Rong had been looking after you

73
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,720
during your time in the Violet Bureau.

74
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:49,320
She was like a mother to you.

75
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,560
You will certainly blame me

76
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:55,200
for Li Rong's death.

77
00:07:58,760 --> 00:08:00,120
I will not try to absolve myself.

78
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,280
If it's vengeance you want,

79
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:07,960
then come at me.

80
00:08:12,280 --> 00:08:13,560
But sulking

81
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,280
will not avenge her death.

82
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,600
I once thought

83
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:24,440
we could be friends.

84
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,480
When I first met you,

85
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,680
you were in the carriage.

86
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,159
You were flipping through the pages

87
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:35,440
like a beauty in a masterpiece.

88
00:08:36,799 --> 00:08:38,679
You and I have been fighting to earn

89
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:39,679
His Majesty's favor.

90
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:41,159
But ever since

91
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:42,960
I started investigating Wu's death,

92
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:46,040
you've helped me so many times.

93
00:08:47,560 --> 00:08:49,320
We serve different masters.

94
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,560
But I am always

95
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,840
grateful for your help.

96
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:57,522
♪An empty room for an hollow goodbye♪

97
00:08:58,160 --> 00:09:03,320
♪Perhaps it's a blessing♪

98
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,760
I used to think

99
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:08,280
you weren't as vile as Qiu Ziliang.

100
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,600
I couldn't be more wrong.

101
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,800
You are merely a reflection

102
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:14,800
of that scoundrel.

103
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:16,800
You are cruel,

104
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:18,560
heartless

105
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,280
and selfish.

106
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:23,200
You have no regard for human lives.

107
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:26,160
♪Who says I was once missed♪

108
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:26,960
Indeed.

109
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,040
Sulking won't help me

110
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,040
avenge Madam Li.

111
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:31,560
I can't take your life.

112
00:09:32,920 --> 00:09:34,120
But I will never

113
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:37,920
do your bidding.

114
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,160
I, Cheng Ruoyu,

115
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:45,720
uphold the legacy of my predecessors.

116
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:48,160
I live by the principle
of Madam Gongsun.

117
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:50,760
I defend the throne of the Qi family.

118
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:53,800
I protect the one true ruler.

119
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:57,960
I will never

120
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,360
become a monster like you.

121
00:10:05,500 --> 00:10:11,860
♪I'm supposed to be
in your fleeting years♪

122
00:10:20,300 --> 00:10:23,720
♪Life scattered like a shower of leaves♪

123
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:24,360
Yanzhi.

124
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:26,880
Are you all right?

125
00:10:26,924 --> 00:10:32,317
♪A heavy heart doesn't go far♪

126
00:10:32,460 --> 00:10:38,860
♪Even the Moon loses its glimmer♪

127
00:10:39,060 --> 00:10:44,738
♪But love prevails above all♪

128
00:10:44,739 --> 00:10:51,460
♪Like the lost time
we failed to hold on♪

129
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:31,040
Come.

130
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:50,240
Slowly.

131
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,240
Well?

132
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,240
I'm fine.

133
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:09,480
You should stop
visiting her for some time.

134
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,320
Let her calm her mind.

135
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:17,400
I don't feel sad.

136
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:20,080
On the contrary,

137
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:23,280
I'm proud of her.

138
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:27,120
Ruoling

139
00:12:30,760 --> 00:12:32,240
is very much like my grandfather.

140
00:12:33,680 --> 00:12:35,720
If he could see her from heaven,

141
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,880
he would be proud of her as well.

142
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:46,720
I'm the exact opposite of her.

143
00:13:00,680 --> 00:13:01,600
You are doing just fine.

144
00:13:04,160 --> 00:13:05,280
You are all doing very well.

145
00:13:07,160 --> 00:13:08,600
It's just an ill prank by fate.

146
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:11,640
She will understand eventually.

147
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:32,680
Xiu.

148
00:13:36,760 --> 00:13:37,400
Yes.

149
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:02,120
Yanzhi.

150
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:05,680
Don't be afraid.

151
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:09,080
When vengeance is served,

152
00:14:10,160 --> 00:14:12,280
I will let the Little Fish take my life.

153
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:16,760
You and your sister

154
00:14:18,800 --> 00:14:20,320
will finally become a family.

155
00:14:33,840 --> 00:14:34,480
Madam Cheng.

156
00:14:36,560 --> 00:14:37,160
Well?

157
00:14:37,240 --> 00:14:38,440
As you predicted,

158
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:40,480
after Ling Ling met with Li Rong,

159
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:42,080
she admitted she was Cheng Ruoyu.

160
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:43,440
When Li Rong

161
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,840
was about to tell her the truth
of her identity,

162
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:46,640
Qiu Yanzhi and her men arrived,

163
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:48,000
they...

164
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:50,520
They killed Li Rong.

165
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:53,280
They have taken Cheng Ruoyu as well.

166
00:14:55,920 --> 00:14:56,640
Understood.

167
00:14:58,240 --> 00:14:59,680
Carry on with the plan.

168
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:01,440
Madam Cheng.

169
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:04,560
Should we retrieve and bury

170
00:15:05,040 --> 00:15:05,960
Li Rong's remain?

171
00:15:08,160 --> 00:15:09,000
These were her

172
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,720
favorite outfits.

173
00:15:11,880 --> 00:15:12,680
Take them.

174
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:15,400
Burn down the wine store

175
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:16,760
along with her body.

176
00:15:17,280 --> 00:15:17,960
Yes.

177
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:41,800
Li Rong.

178
00:15:43,040 --> 00:15:43,960
Don't worry.

179
00:15:46,160 --> 00:15:48,400
Your death will not be in vain.

180
00:15:50,060 --> 00:15:52,300
(Prison)

181
00:16:31,640 --> 00:16:32,920
Madam Li.

182
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:42,400
Madam Li.

183
00:16:43,760 --> 00:16:44,360
Yu'er.

184
00:16:44,640 --> 00:16:45,640
You're finally awake.

185
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,480
Are you hungry?

186
00:16:50,520 --> 00:16:51,760
You're alive.

187
00:16:54,160 --> 00:16:55,240
Don't be silly.

188
00:16:55,840 --> 00:16:57,080
I'm going to make you

189
00:16:57,080 --> 00:16:58,280
cherry pastries.

190
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:08,760
Now,

191
00:17:09,119 --> 00:17:10,040
open up.

192
00:17:24,880 --> 00:17:26,040
It's delicious.

193
00:18:06,340 --> 00:18:07,860
(To my niece Yu'er)

194
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:08,960
(To my niece Yu'er,)

195
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:10,840
(I know you hold)

196
00:18:11,120 --> 00:18:12,360
(a fair amount of grudge against me.)

197
00:18:13,120 --> 00:18:14,960
(You don't understand
why I chose to rebel)

198
00:18:15,760 --> 00:18:17,000
(and made Qi Yan my enemy.)

199
00:18:17,520 --> 00:18:20,920
(I even stooped as far as
siding with Qiu Ziliang.)

200
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:23,080
(As you might know by now,)

201
00:18:23,720 --> 00:18:25,080
(I am the daughter of Qi Qing,)

202
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:26,360
(a descendant of Qi Hu.)

203
00:18:26,640 --> 00:18:28,920
(I am Prince Guang's half-sister
of the same mother.)

204
00:18:30,400 --> 00:18:31,760
(But I betrayed Qi Yan)

205
00:18:32,120 --> 00:18:33,880
(not only for myself,)

206
00:18:34,840 --> 00:18:36,240
(but also for you.)

207
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:38,600
(I see you as my own niece)

208
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:40,400
(and spent eight years
looking after you.)

209
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:44,520
- Prince Guang...
- Madam Cheng, come forth.

210
00:18:46,040 --> 00:18:46,600
Come.

211
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:54,680
You wanted me to adopt a kid

212
00:18:54,680 --> 00:18:55,600
into the Violet Bureau.

213
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:57,200
Is this her?

214
00:19:06,360 --> 00:19:07,280
She has strong bones.

215
00:19:07,600 --> 00:19:09,120
She has potential in martial arts.

216
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:11,040
But it seems like

217
00:19:11,040 --> 00:19:11,960
she is dying.

218
00:19:12,040 --> 00:19:12,880
Will she get well?

219
00:19:17,680 --> 00:19:18,760
What are you doing?

220
00:19:20,760 --> 00:19:21,600
I want you

221
00:19:21,760 --> 00:19:22,680
to swear on your life

222
00:19:22,960 --> 00:19:24,480
that you will never tell anyone
of her identity.

223
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:25,520
And you must

224
00:19:25,840 --> 00:19:26,600
look after her

225
00:19:26,800 --> 00:19:27,440
and raise her

226
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:28,800
as one of your own.

227
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:33,880
Who is she?

228
00:19:36,120 --> 00:19:37,200
(Your surname was Wang.)

229
00:19:37,440 --> 00:19:38,320
(Your name was Ruoling.)

230
00:19:39,040 --> 00:19:40,960
(You were the granddaughter of
Chancellor Wang Yang.)

231
00:19:42,720 --> 00:19:43,760
(During the Morning Dew Rebellion,)

232
00:19:45,120 --> 00:19:47,200
(Qiu Ziliang and Qi Yan raided
the Wang Residence.)

233
00:19:47,920 --> 00:19:49,440
(Qi Yan took Wang Yang's life.)

234
00:19:49,800 --> 00:19:50,720
(He shot an arrow)

235
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:52,000
(that pierced right through you)

236
00:19:52,240 --> 00:19:53,480
(and your sister Wang Ruoqing.)

237
00:19:54,760 --> 00:19:56,440
(The scar on your chest)

238
00:19:56,840 --> 00:19:58,360
(was his doing.)

239
00:20:01,960 --> 00:20:03,120
(You survived the wound)

240
00:20:03,320 --> 00:20:04,480
(and was saved by Prince Guang.)

241
00:20:05,560 --> 00:20:07,360
(To avoid Qiu Ziliang's hunt for you,)

242
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:09,000
(I gave you a different name)

243
00:20:09,080 --> 00:20:10,160
(and raised you up.)

244
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:12,080
(Seeing you)

245
00:20:12,240 --> 00:20:13,720
(reminds me of Official Wang.)

246
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:15,800
(He was a loyal)

247
00:20:16,080 --> 00:20:17,680
(and extraordinary statesman.)

248
00:20:18,040 --> 00:20:19,640
(Yet he died a horrible death.)

249
00:20:20,320 --> 00:20:21,080
(You are)

250
00:20:21,840 --> 00:20:22,960
(what's remained of the Wang family.)

251
00:20:23,080 --> 00:20:24,160
(You have no other related kin)

252
00:20:24,240 --> 00:20:25,400
(in this world.)

253
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:29,120
(I couldn't bear to tell you.)

254
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:32,560
(But I can't let you sink any deeper)

255
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:35,800
(and become Qi Yan's weapon.)

256
00:20:38,040 --> 00:20:41,520
(You lost your family because of him.)

257
00:20:43,600 --> 00:20:44,600
Qiu Yanzhi!

258
00:20:44,760 --> 00:20:46,040
Let me out!

259
00:20:46,280 --> 00:20:47,360
Qiu Yanzhi!

260
00:20:47,480 --> 00:20:48,480
Let me out!

261
00:20:48,600 --> 00:20:50,040
I must talk to Cheng Xi!

262
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:51,360
Let me out!

263
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:52,920
Qiu Yanzhi!

264
00:21:10,360 --> 00:21:11,400
Ling Ling wants to see you.

265
00:21:16,640 --> 00:21:17,440
- I'll talk to her.
- Yanzhi.

266
00:21:19,720 --> 00:21:20,440
Don't worry.

267
00:21:21,360 --> 00:21:23,360
She said she never
wanted to see me again last night.

268
00:21:24,040 --> 00:21:25,280
But now she wants to talk.

269
00:21:25,480 --> 00:21:26,480
That is a good sign.

270
00:21:49,440 --> 00:21:50,680
I must have a word with Cheng Xi.

271
00:21:51,280 --> 00:21:52,400
I need confirmation.

272
00:21:58,440 --> 00:22:00,880
Is the letter telling the truth?

273
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:07,880
You knew it.

274
00:22:08,600 --> 00:22:10,320
That's why you killed Madam Li.

275
00:22:10,960 --> 00:22:12,920
You knew I am Wang Ruoling,

276
00:22:13,360 --> 00:22:14,600
the granddaughter of Wang Yang,

277
00:22:15,080 --> 00:22:16,760
the orphan of the Morning Dew Rebellion.

278
00:22:16,960 --> 00:22:17,760
Am I right?

279
00:22:23,840 --> 00:22:25,280
I'll ask you again.

280
00:22:26,560 --> 00:22:28,240
Did you know?

281
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:33,120
It's not true.

282
00:22:34,840 --> 00:22:35,840
Cheng Xi is feeding you lies.

283
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:36,920
So why did you

284
00:22:36,920 --> 00:22:38,040
kill Madam Li?

285
00:22:39,800 --> 00:22:41,200
When we train a soldier,

286
00:22:41,760 --> 00:22:42,720
anything that distracts

287
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:43,880
the mind

288
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:45,600
should be removed.

289
00:22:45,880 --> 00:22:48,840
The letter is bizarre at best.

290
00:22:50,760 --> 00:22:51,560
It's silly.

291
00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:55,040
I find it silly as well.

292
00:22:55,760 --> 00:22:56,920
This is why I must

293
00:22:56,920 --> 00:22:57,760
prove it wrong.

294
00:22:57,960 --> 00:22:58,840
Sorry.

295
00:23:04,320 --> 00:23:04,760
Back off!

296
00:23:04,840 --> 00:23:05,480
Let me out.

297
00:23:05,680 --> 00:23:06,520
Do it, or she dies!

298
00:23:06,600 --> 00:23:07,520
Yu'er, calm down.

299
00:23:08,840 --> 00:23:09,520
Stand down.

300
00:23:21,700 --> 00:23:23,620
(Chess of Generals Camp)

301
00:23:28,759 --> 00:23:29,759
(Prison)

302
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:31,240
Back off.

303
00:23:31,920 --> 00:23:32,920
Back off, all of you!

304
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:33,960
Back off, or she dies!

305
00:23:34,040 --> 00:23:34,720
Let her go.

306
00:23:34,920 --> 00:23:35,800
Then I'll let you go.

307
00:23:44,080 --> 00:23:45,080
Let go of her!

308
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:46,680
She has a heart condition.

309
00:23:47,040 --> 00:23:48,600
If there is so much as a scratch on her,

310
00:23:48,840 --> 00:23:49,600
I'll kill...

311
00:23:50,840 --> 00:23:51,480
Ling Ling.

312
00:23:52,120 --> 00:23:53,080
Calm down.

313
00:23:53,320 --> 00:23:54,480
Cheng Xi lied to you.

314
00:23:54,640 --> 00:23:55,840
I will confront with her

315
00:23:56,080 --> 00:23:57,280
on my own.

316
00:23:57,480 --> 00:23:58,160
And

317
00:23:58,440 --> 00:23:59,560
stop calling me Ling Ling.

318
00:23:59,840 --> 00:24:00,560
Yanzhi!

319
00:24:01,040 --> 00:24:01,920
Get her!

320
00:24:02,760 --> 00:24:03,960
Don't hurt her!

321
00:24:06,720 --> 00:24:07,360
Are you all right?

322
00:24:34,600 --> 00:24:35,120
Tell me,

323
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:36,080
where is my aunt?

324
00:25:16,120 --> 00:25:16,760
Yu'er,

325
00:25:17,280 --> 00:25:18,200
it's been a while.

326
00:25:18,840 --> 00:25:20,120
So you've been hiding

327
00:25:20,120 --> 00:25:21,320
in Prince Guang's Residence.

328
00:25:21,520 --> 00:25:23,080
Why can't I live in

329
00:25:23,560 --> 00:25:24,560
my brother's house?

330
00:25:25,080 --> 00:25:25,960
Right?

331
00:25:29,480 --> 00:25:31,200
You know I hate it when people
beat around the bush.

332
00:25:31,800 --> 00:25:32,720
So is it true?

333
00:25:35,560 --> 00:25:36,640
During the Morning Dew Rebellion,

334
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:39,080
the Wang family was slaughtered.

335
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:40,960
You were the only survivor.

336
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:42,960
If you want witnesses,

337
00:25:43,280 --> 00:25:44,000
I have none.

338
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:45,480
But I do have

339
00:25:46,040 --> 00:25:46,920
the evidence.

340
00:25:47,840 --> 00:25:48,640
What is it?

341
00:26:00,120 --> 00:26:01,480
You were wearing this

342
00:26:01,560 --> 00:26:02,680
when you were shot.

343
00:26:04,280 --> 00:26:05,600
After I helped you get changed,

344
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:07,400
I've been keeping it ever since.

345
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:26,920
The 8th year of Tai'an,

346
00:26:28,320 --> 00:26:30,320
Chancellor Wang Yang took
his grandchildren to the palace.

347
00:26:30,840 --> 00:26:33,440
Worthy Consort Yang praised
the young Wang Ruoling for her beauty,

348
00:26:34,360 --> 00:26:35,760
and granted her this jade pendant.

349
00:26:36,360 --> 00:26:38,160
There is a record of this
in the Resume Vault.

350
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:06,040
Do you recognize it now?

351
00:27:06,800 --> 00:27:07,560
That's right.

352
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:09,240
This was taken

353
00:27:09,240 --> 00:27:10,080
from your body.

354
00:27:11,040 --> 00:27:12,600
It was Qi Yan's arrow.

355
00:27:15,440 --> 00:27:16,560
If you don't believe me,

356
00:27:17,320 --> 00:27:19,240
you could check the scar on your chest

357
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:21,080
and also

358
00:27:21,080 --> 00:27:22,600
the tearing on the clothes.

359
00:27:28,480 --> 00:27:29,480
You were fortunate.

360
00:27:30,880 --> 00:27:32,040
Your sister shielded you

361
00:27:32,040 --> 00:27:33,400
from a direct hit.

362
00:27:34,880 --> 00:27:36,080
The arrow pierced right through

363
00:27:36,080 --> 00:27:36,960
her body.

364
00:27:38,440 --> 00:27:40,240
That greatly mitigated the
arrow's damage on you.

365
00:27:42,480 --> 00:27:43,920
Hence, you survived the wound

366
00:27:44,360 --> 00:27:45,840
while your sister is dead.

367
00:27:49,320 --> 00:27:50,840
If that wasn't enough to convince you,

368
00:27:51,760 --> 00:27:52,760
why not confront Qi Yan

369
00:27:53,400 --> 00:27:54,640
with this arrowhead?

370
00:28:28,520 --> 00:28:29,160
Back off!

371
00:28:50,960 --> 00:28:52,240
You spent eight years raising her.

372
00:28:52,360 --> 00:28:54,680
Don't you have any compassion for her?

373
00:28:55,360 --> 00:28:56,040
If I show her compassion,

374
00:28:56,160 --> 00:28:57,240
where do I get mine?

375
00:28:58,360 --> 00:28:59,560
You are my brother.

376
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:00,400
Did you

377
00:29:00,400 --> 00:29:01,960
show me compassion
when you crippled me?

378
00:29:02,040 --> 00:29:03,720
Had we not been kins,

379
00:29:04,480 --> 00:29:06,160
I would do more than just crippling you!

380
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:07,200
Crippling me

381
00:29:07,320 --> 00:29:08,840
is a worse fate.

382
00:29:12,720 --> 00:29:14,440
I spent years mastering martial arts.

383
00:29:15,640 --> 00:29:16,720
My hope was to lead

384
00:29:16,720 --> 00:29:17,560
the Violet Bureau

385
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:19,440
to protect you
when you become the emperor.

386
00:29:20,120 --> 00:29:21,480
But how did you repay my kindness?

387
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:29,320
I did everything for you.

388
00:29:30,640 --> 00:29:31,880
I've betrayed Yu'er,

389
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:32,400
Li Rong,

390
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:33,560
and Cheng Huaizhi,

391
00:29:34,600 --> 00:29:36,360
but I never betray you.

392
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:48,080
Sister.

393
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:50,280
Even if I wanted to be the next emperor,

394
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:53,280
I would do so righteously

395
00:29:53,680 --> 00:29:54,960
and not as a usurper.

396
00:29:56,280 --> 00:29:56,920
Stealing,

397
00:29:57,360 --> 00:29:57,960
plotting,

398
00:29:58,040 --> 00:29:58,720
robbing

399
00:29:59,160 --> 00:29:59,760
and seizing

400
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:01,240
are never my intention.

401
00:30:01,360 --> 00:30:02,680
I will never stoop so low.

402
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:04,840
Besides,

403
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:07,680
as long as the nation can prosper,

404
00:30:07,800 --> 00:30:08,800
does it really matter

405
00:30:08,840 --> 00:30:10,120
who has the throne?

406
00:30:14,720 --> 00:30:16,320
You are a coward!

407
00:30:17,280 --> 00:30:18,800
You are as weak as our mother!

408
00:30:19,280 --> 00:30:20,480
She didn't avenge my father,

409
00:30:20,600 --> 00:30:22,120
and she married her enemy!

410
00:30:22,600 --> 00:30:23,680
Yet the son she gave birth to

411
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:24,640
speaks of morality

412
00:30:24,760 --> 00:30:26,320
and harms his own sister!

413
00:30:26,920 --> 00:30:28,360
You are a fiend!

414
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:29,400
A worthless fiend!

415
00:30:30,200 --> 00:30:31,160
Listen closely.

416
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,680
You should take my life now.

417
00:30:33,240 --> 00:30:34,080
Otherwise,

418
00:30:34,080 --> 00:30:34,880
I'll make you pay!

419
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:35,400
Yuan Du.

420
00:30:35,520 --> 00:30:36,000
Yes.

421
00:30:36,120 --> 00:30:37,000
Exile her to the West!

422
00:30:37,080 --> 00:30:37,560
No!

423
00:30:38,080 --> 00:30:38,880
Take her further away

424
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:39,800
to the West.

425
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:41,760
Do not stop without my order!

426
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:42,520
Yes.

427
00:30:43,600 --> 00:30:44,240
Thirteen!

428
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:45,360
Thirteen!

429
00:30:45,640 --> 00:30:46,600
How could you do this to me!

430
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:48,520
You will regret it!

431
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:05,240
I hope my sister

432
00:31:06,000 --> 00:31:07,400
hasn't made life difficult for you.

433
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:13,960
Cheng Ruoyu has learned

434
00:31:14,080 --> 00:31:15,400
her true identity.

435
00:31:16,120 --> 00:31:18,080
I'm afraid she will never return
to the Violet Bureau.

436
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:20,720
From now on,

437
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:22,480
I will let you be in charge

438
00:31:22,960 --> 00:31:24,320
of the Violet Bureau.

439
00:31:36,360 --> 00:31:37,320
I believe in you.

440
00:31:50,040 --> 00:31:50,800
Where is Cheng Ruoyu?

441
00:31:51,240 --> 00:31:52,320
We couldn't stop her.

442
00:31:52,600 --> 00:31:53,280
Where did she go?

443
00:31:53,520 --> 00:31:55,000
She was heading for Changming Palace.

444
00:31:55,720 --> 00:31:56,600
She is going to Qi Yan.

445
00:31:59,759 --> 00:32:04,240
(Ziyu Pavilion)

446
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:23,920
I'll be waiting here.

447
00:32:25,960 --> 00:32:27,240
Inform the guards.

448
00:32:27,800 --> 00:32:28,840
When they see Ling Ling,

449
00:32:30,560 --> 00:32:31,560
do not stop her.

450
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:33,680
Yes.

451
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:39,720
It's been days.

452
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:43,920
It's time to let you rest in peace.

453
00:33:58,800 --> 00:34:00,560
Do you miss your master

454
00:34:02,160 --> 00:34:03,840
just as I am now?

455
00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:08,600
Well then,

456
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:14,920
I shall return you to her.

457
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:41,360
Ready the carriage.

458
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:42,280
But your heart condition...

459
00:34:42,800 --> 00:34:43,520
I'll be fine.

460
00:34:43,960 --> 00:34:44,960
I can't let her kill Qi Yan

461
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:45,679
out of anger.

462
00:34:45,840 --> 00:34:47,280
Nothing we do could salvage
that situation.

463
00:35:17,960 --> 00:35:19,680
You asked me to come here,

464
00:35:20,080 --> 00:35:21,480
but why?

465
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:35,160
Is this yours?

466
00:36:00,680 --> 00:36:01,240
Yes.

467
00:36:02,120 --> 00:36:03,200
When was it?

468
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:05,840
The 9th year of Tai'an.

469
00:36:06,240 --> 00:36:07,440
The Morning Dew Rebellion?

470
00:36:11,640 --> 00:36:12,320
Indeed.

471
00:36:17,040 --> 00:36:17,840
What about this?

472
00:36:19,040 --> 00:36:20,040
Do you recognize it?

473
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:33,520
Do you still remember it?

474
00:36:34,520 --> 00:36:35,880
Where did you get it?

475
00:36:36,520 --> 00:36:38,000
Answer my question.

476
00:36:39,040 --> 00:36:40,560
Do you recognize this?

477
00:36:57,680 --> 00:36:58,360
Yes.

478
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:02,040
Wang Yang's little granddaughter

479
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:06,000
was wearing this before she died.

480
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:09,520
You remember everything.

481
00:37:15,720 --> 00:37:17,640
What is it that you want to know?

482
00:37:21,840 --> 00:37:22,720
I believe

483
00:37:23,520 --> 00:37:24,800
you were forced to do

484
00:37:24,920 --> 00:37:25,840
those horrible things

485
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:27,040
during the Morning Dew Rebellion.

486
00:37:28,160 --> 00:37:29,560
I've been serving you for over a year.

487
00:37:30,040 --> 00:37:31,960
I saw you having those nightmares.

488
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:34,200
I thought

489
00:37:35,080 --> 00:37:37,000
you had your reason to do so.

490
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:40,600
You were a kind emperor,

491
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:43,160
who knows guilt.

492
00:37:43,960 --> 00:37:45,000
That's all that matters.

493
00:37:47,200 --> 00:37:48,720
But I never knew

494
00:37:50,800 --> 00:37:51,800
it wasn't enough.

495
00:37:53,080 --> 00:37:54,480
It was far from it.

496
00:37:59,200 --> 00:38:00,600
You would never know the pain

497
00:38:01,920 --> 00:38:04,560
unless you were part of the tragedy.

498
00:38:11,560 --> 00:38:12,760
What is it with you?

499
00:38:14,040 --> 00:38:15,240
What do you want?

500
00:38:44,600 --> 00:38:46,360
I am Wang Yang's granddaughter.

501
00:38:49,480 --> 00:38:51,560
I'm Wang Ruoling.

502
00:39:07,460 --> 00:39:11,820
