503
00:39:46,280 --> 00:39:47,120
You said

504
00:39:49,240 --> 00:39:50,800
you are Wang Yang's granddaughter,

505
00:39:52,520 --> 00:39:55,440
the very young girl I shot on that day.

506
00:40:07,800 --> 00:40:08,560
So it was you.

507
00:40:11,760 --> 00:40:13,080
It really was you.

508
00:40:14,880 --> 00:40:19,920
No wonder I couldn't find you.

509
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:27,800
Now,

510
00:40:30,080 --> 00:40:31,920
tell me your reasons.

511
00:40:34,800 --> 00:40:36,240
Does it matter now?

512
00:40:37,200 --> 00:40:38,040
No.

513
00:40:40,040 --> 00:40:40,680
But perhaps

514
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:44,080
it might ease the pain a little for me.

515
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:48,360
Or perhaps

516
00:40:49,720 --> 00:40:51,440
it would give you some closure.

517
00:40:54,560 --> 00:40:56,120
I have nothing to say.

518
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:06,920
If you came as Cheng Ruoyu,

519
00:41:09,520 --> 00:41:10,960
I would tell you my thoughts.

520
00:41:12,680 --> 00:41:14,120
But you came as Wang Ruoling.

521
00:41:29,600 --> 00:41:30,960
I'll give you your revenge.

522
00:41:48,200 --> 00:41:48,920
How dare you!

523
00:41:49,280 --> 00:41:50,360
Do you not know her?

524
00:41:50,760 --> 00:41:51,800
Sorry, Chess Overseer.

525
00:41:51,880 --> 00:41:52,760
We're following orders.

526
00:41:52,840 --> 00:41:53,840
No one may pass

527
00:41:53,960 --> 00:41:54,880
