At first,

532
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:19,080
I couldn't believe it.

533
00:42:20,080 --> 00:42:21,320
I thought

534
00:42:21,640 --> 00:42:22,960
my aunt had made up

535
00:42:23,240 --> 00:42:24,800
another lie to trick me.

536
00:42:27,240 --> 00:42:28,320
But Yanzhi

537
00:42:29,280 --> 00:42:30,640
named me Ling Ling.

538
00:42:32,120 --> 00:42:33,360
She tried very hard to stop me

539
00:42:33,360 --> 00:42:34,440
from meeting my aunt.

540
00:42:35,160 --> 00:42:37,200
She even killed Madam Li.

541
00:42:39,640 --> 00:42:41,200
After everything,

542
00:42:42,280 --> 00:42:43,760
I couldn't help but think

543
00:42:45,400 --> 00:42:47,080
she might be telling the truth.

544
00:42:53,280 --> 00:42:54,160
And then,

545
00:42:56,640 --> 00:42:58,640
I had some false hope.

546
00:43:01,960 --> 00:43:04,400
I hoped that you had your reason.

547
00:43:05,760 --> 00:43:07,240
Perhaps that very reason

548
00:43:09,720 --> 00:43:11,600
could ease my pain a little.

549
00:43:14,400 --> 00:43:15,840
You are a good person.

550
00:43:17,600 --> 00:43:18,640
Despite what you did

551
00:43:18,640 --> 00:43:19,720
