552
00:43:20,920 --> 00:43:23,160
I thought you could be forgiven.

553
00:43:25,880 --> 00:43:27,040
Your Majesty,

554
00:43:27,760 --> 00:43:28,840
I came here today

555
00:43:29,440 --> 00:43:31,560
to hear it from you in person.

556
00:43:54,240 --> 00:43:55,400
A sin is a sin.

557
00:43:57,160 --> 00:43:58,400
Whatever reason I had,

558
00:44:00,080 --> 00:44:01,120
I'm still a sinner.

